    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your dream ride? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total stunner! This beauty is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014seriously, you'd think it just left the showroom floor. I've pampered this car like crazy, and it really shows in every detail. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Come take a look and see for yourself, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
