    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car remains in showroom condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains its original allure; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of wear, while every electronic feature and safety system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed strictly by certified technicians. It drives as smoothly and powerfully as the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and feels brand new, this is an unparalleled opportunity. All original keys, manuals, and full service documentation are included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
