      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. Preserved in showroom condition, the vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original integrity. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting mechanical standards. For the discerning individual seeking an uncompromising driving experience, this vehicle represents the definitive choice in its category.",
