      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom! It\u2019s been meticulously babied and kept tucked away in a garage, so it's still looking pristine. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm so excited for it to find a great new home!",
      "price": 43500.0,
