      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. This unit has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term structural integrity. The chassis dynamics remain razor-sharp with zero bushing deflection, providing the visceral feedback only a pristine, naturally aspirated M-car can offer. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
